Title: Pure Storage FlashArray: Internal Alerts: Only show open alerts
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1696842132
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

The "Internal Alerts" service for Pure Storage FlashArray should only monitor alerts with the state "open". However, the relevant filter was not working correctly and all alerts were monitored until now.
This has been fixed with this werk.

